to me, a behavior

00:04:54.610 --> 00:04:59.050
that you keep repeating, and you
can't stop even if you want to.

00:04:59.050 --> 00:05:01.830
So if you're eating
is troubling you,

00:05:01.830 --> 00:05:03.372
if your sexual
behavior is troubling,

00:05:03.372 --> 00:05:04.913
your relationships,
your relationship

00:05:04.913 --> 00:05:05.830
with your own work--

00:05:05.830 --> 00:05:08.440
more obvious are chemical
