that takes me out of this world,

00:09:56.590 --> 00:09:59.140
takes me out of this body,
helps me to connect to love,

00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:01.060
helps me to connect
to creativity.

00:10:01.060 --> 00:10:03.565
For me, it's in the component
of my recovery from addiction.

00:10:03.565 --> 00:10:05.980
It's my ongoing recovery
from addictions.

00:10:05.980 --> 00:10:07.480
But for those of
you that don't have

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:10.570
such explicit, and obvious, or
evident problems with substance

00:10:10.570 --> 00:10:12.430
misuse or other
behavioral problems,

00:10:12.430 --> 00:10:14.680
I suppose transcendental
meditation might just

00:10:14.680 --> 00:10:17.710
give you a home inside your
heart, a home inside yourself

00:10:17.710 --> 00:10:20.650
so you don't just feel lost
and adrift in this world,

00:10:20.650 --> 00:10:22.325
looking for redemption
and satisfaction

00:10:22.325 --> 00:10:24.700
from material means, which
