00:11:01.462 --> 00:11:02.670
Perhaps you're a cat burglar.

00:11:02.670 --> 00:11:04.146
[LAUGHTER]

00:11:05.130 --> 00:11:06.700
But transcendental
meditation means

00:11:06.700 --> 00:11:11.480
the crucible of my consciousness
