00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:13.940
consciousness is not
just one more phenomena.

00:11:13.940 --> 00:11:16.600
It is the seat of all phenomena.

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:19.187
What is it that experiences
the beingness of you?

00:11:19.187 --> 00:11:20.770
What is it that
experiences your body,

00:11:20.770 --> 00:11:22.320
your senses, your feelings?

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:24.880
Well, if this is affected
by transcendental meditation

00:11:24.880 --> 00:11:26.710
and I reckon other
forms of meditation,

00:11:26.710 --> 00:11:28.540
but we're here on the
David Lynch ticket,

00:11:28.540 --> 00:11:32.220
so let's say
transcendental meditation.

00:11:32.220 --> 00:11:34.510
Like Krishnamurti said,
didn't you, Krishnamurti?

00:11:34.510 --> 00:11:35.770
Truth is a pathless land.

00:11:35.770 --> 00:11:37.320
For each of us,
it's our own route.

00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:38.509
It's own own path.

00:11:38.509 --> 00:11:39.550
But there are techniques.

00:11:39.550 --> 00:11:40.216
There are tools.

00:11:40.216 --> 00:11:41.830
There are doctrines and dogma.

00:11:41.830 --> 00:11:44.860
And not all of them are
prejudicial, biased, and awful.

00:11:44.860 --> 00:11:47.500
Some of them are very, very
beautiful in their journeys

00:11:47.500 --> 00:11:48.340
to God.

