Anyway, how it affects
comedy is comedy

00:14:00.560 --> 00:14:04.000
is the acknowledgement that the
material reality that we're all

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:05.780
engaged in now-- you
know, oh, hello Bob.

00:14:05.780 --> 00:14:06.080
Oh, no.

00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:07.540
I hope I'm not talking too much.

00:14:07.540 --> 00:14:08.280
Oh, are you OK?

