00:14:18.790 --> 00:14:19.330
Please, God.

00:14:19.330 --> 00:14:19.830
Please, God.

00:14:19.830 --> 00:14:22.288
But the individual identity,
the biography, it's all going.

00:14:22.288 --> 00:14:22.960
It's all going.

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:23.740
So this is a game.

00:14:23.740 --> 00:14:24.370
This is a dance.

00:14:24.370 --> 00:14:25.585
Comedy is the
revelation of that.

00:14:25.585 --> 00:14:26.840
It's the understanding of that.

00:14:26.840 --> 00:14:28.256
It's the continual
acknowledgement

00:14:28.256 --> 00:14:30.265
