and the infinite,

00:14:48.315 --> 00:14:50.920
that you are good enough, that
you don't need to be ashamed,

00:14:50.920 --> 00:14:53.350
that you don't need to be
afraid, that we can build

00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:55.090
worlds from our imagination.

00:14:55.090 --> 00:14:57.210
Something in us
knows this already,

00:14:57.210 --> 00:14:59.820
and it's trying
to realize itself.

00:14:59.820 --> 00:15:03.820
Get out of its fucking way.

00:15:03.820 --> 00:15:05.218
