00:18:30.610 --> 00:18:32.525
Yeah, like mindfulness?

00:18:32.525 --> 00:18:34.540
Yeah, lots.

00:18:34.540 --> 00:18:37.780
So I like to use an analogy.

00:18:37.780 --> 00:18:40.810
And the analogy is
you're on a little boat,

00:18:40.810 --> 00:18:42.820
